snippet.title: [NOT MUGEN] NAMCO SUPER HEROES demo - version NSH1021.EXE (2016/09/18)
snippet.description:
[NOT MUGEN] NAMCO SUPER HEROES demo - version NSH1021.EXE (2016/09/18)

Thanks to my MUGEN friend, Gladiacloud, I got to know that hiro has updated his cool classic NAMCO SUPER HEROES from 2009 to 2016:

http://hiro.blue.coocan.jp/products/NSH/NSH.html

Now I take a chance to record the game play of hiro's update of his cool classic NAMCO SUPER HEROES!
